OL,3,CThree men sentenced for attempted
OL,4,Cmurder of man in Bristol on Boxing Day
OL,6,FThree men have been sentenced for the
OL,7,Fattempted murder of a man in Bristol
OL,8,Fon Boxing Day in 2023.
OL,10,FThe victim, who was aged 24, suffered
OL,11,Fstab wounds which nearly killed him.
OL,12,FHe has had to learn to walk and talk
OL,13,Fagain as part of his recovery.
OL,15,FFour people have now been sentenced to
OL,16,Fa combined total of 75 years for their
OL,17,Fparts in the stabbing.
