OL,3,CThree men sentenced for attempted
OL,4,Cmurder of man in Bristol on Boxing Day
OL,6,FOn 22 December, Reuben Fay, 20, of
OL,7,FLockleaze was told he would spend 23
OL,8,Fyears in detention. Tayshon Graham,
OL,9,F21, of Easton has also been jailed for
OL,10,F23 years and Cain Henderson, 24, of
OL,11,FEastville, has been sentenced to 23
OL,12,Fyears in prison.
OL,14,FAll three had previously admitted
OL,15,Fcausing grievous bodily harm with
OL,16,Fintent but denied attempted murder.
OL,17,FHowever the jury did not agree.
