OL,6,FA fourth man, Ajay Edwards, 22, from
OL,7,FSlough, had previously admitted
OL,8,Fcausing grievous bodily harm with
OL,9,Fintent and was sentenced to six years
OL,10,Fin prison.
OL,12,F'Tit for tat attacks'
OL,14,FThe jury was told the attack was part
OL,15,Fof a string of 'tit for tat' attacks
OL,16,Fbetween the St Paul's gang the 2-4's
OL,17,Fand their rival group the 1-6's in
OL,18,FFishponds.
