OL,3,CThree men sentenced for attempted
OL,4,Cmurder of man in Bristol on Boxing Day
OL,6,FThe victim of the attack was a man
OL,7,Ffrom Fishponds who had gone for a meal
OL,8,Fwith friends at a restaurant on
OL,9,FGloucester Road in Bishopston.
OL,11,FGraham, Fay and Edwards entered the
OL,12,Fsame restaurant, keeping their hoods
OL,13,Fup, and sat down for just one minute,
OL,14,Fbefore leaving.
OL,16,FAbout 40 minutes later, they returned
OL,17,Fto Gloucester Road, now with
OL,18,FHenderson, and pursued the victim and
OL,19,Fhis friends as they were leaving the
OL,20,Frestaurant.
