OL,3,CThree men sentenced for attempted
OL,4,Cmurder of man in Bristol on Boxing Day
OL,6,FThe victim tripped and fell in Bishop
OL,7,FRoad. He was then stabbed repeatedly `
OL,8,Fat least seven times ` where he lay,
OL,9,Fthe court heard.
OL,11,FHe suffered a brain injury, and
OL,12,Fmultiple significant wounds to his
OL,13,Fface, neck, shoulder, arm, chest and
OL,14,Fbuttock.
OL,16,FThe attackers fled the scene, and all
OL,17,Fexcept Henderson left Bristol soon
OL,18,Fafterwards, police say.
OL,20,F'Lengthy sentences for young men'
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
