OL,3,CThree men sentenced for attempted
OL,4,Cmurder of man in Bristol on Boxing Day
OL,6,FHis Honour Judge Michael Cullum said
OL,7,Feach of the defendant's personal
OL,8,Fcircumstances were "tragically
OL,9,Fsimilar".
OL,11,FHe said he took account of the
OL,12,Fmitigation of their youth and adverse
OL,13,Fpersonal circumstances when sentencing.
OL,15,FHe added that the sentences were
OL,16,F"substantial" and "very lengthy for
OL,17,Fyoung men" but said he considered each
OL,18,Fto be a dangerous offender.
