OL,6,F"You've ripped that all away" she told
OL,7,Fthe defendants. He's had to learn to
OL,8,Fwalk and talk again, he's lost his
OL,9,Fmemory.
OL,11,F"The saddest part of all of this is
OL,12,Fyou probably can't either tell us why
OL,13,Fyou did it," she added.
